             ZURK I: "The Great Zurkian Empire"                                 This delightful little story is about an adventurer who found himself in        a mystical land of canyons and valleys, boats and hot airships that flew        in the air.                                                                     END                                                                             It is rumored that the story and several sequels were written in honor of       ancient hi-mythology writers of great classic fantasies.                        FINISH                                                                          